OL,3,CWoman's fury after 'corridor care'
OL,4,Cnightmare at hospital
OL,6,FA woman whose partner went missing
OL,7,Ffrom hospital while he was being
OL,8,Ftreated in a corridor is urging the
OL,9,FGovernment to do more to bring down
OL,10,Fwaiting times.
OL,12,FNicholas Sheppard, 75, spent two days
OL,13,Fin a corridor at the William Harvey
OL,14,FHospital in Ashford in September after
OL,15,Fsuffering a head injury during a fall.
OL,17,FOn his second night in hospital, he
OL,18,Fwandered off and spent the following
OL,19,Ftwo days lost. A police search was
OL,20,Flaunched and Mr Sheppard was
OL,21,Feventually found in a wooded area.
