OL,3,CWoman's fury after 'corridor care'
OL,4,Cnightmare at hospital
OL,6,FMr Sheppard's partner, Janet Pott,
OL,7,Fsays he was almost dead and is now on
OL,8,Fa ward after weeks in critical care.
OL,10,FShe believes he would not have been
OL,11,Fable to leave the hospital if he was
OL,12,Fbeing cared for on a ward.
OL,14,FMs Pott described the scene in A&E at
OL,15,Fthe hospital as "like a war-zone."
