OL,3,CWoman's fury after 'corridor care'
OL,4,Cnightmare at hospital
OL,6,FShe said: "The queue was the whole
OL,7,Flength of the corridor. I can't pick
OL,8,Fholes in the staff as they were
OL,9,Fworking under extreme pressure. I
OL,10,Fcan't tell you how difficult it was
OL,11,Ffor them.
OL,13,F"At that point, Nick was fine but it
OL,14,Fwas just the waiting. And in that
OL,15,Fcorridor, there were people in there
OL,16,Fon their own as well.
OL,18,F"Nick had me with him but some people
OL,19,Fhad no one with them and they were
OL,20,Fjust lying there.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
