OL,4,Cnightmare at hospital
OL,6,FJanet said: "At first I thought he'd
OL,7,Fgone to the toilet so I went looking
OL,8,Ffor him and when he wasn't there I
OL,9,Fraised the alarm.
OL,11,F"Members of the security team were
OL,12,Fsearching for him. Someone mentioned
OL,13,FCCTV and I definitely heard him say
OL,14,Fthey couldn't look at the CCTV because
OL,15,Fof data protection.
OL,17,F"Had they done so they would have
OL,18,Fknown Nick had already left the
OL,19,Fhospital."
