OL,6,FA spokesperson for East Kent Hospitals
OL,7,FUniversity NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,8,Fruns William Harvey Hospital, said:
OL,10,F"We sincerely apologise to Mr Sheppard
OL,11,Fand his family. We are working with
OL,12,Fthem to further investigate what
OL,13,Fhappened and how lessons can be
OL,14,Flearned.
