OL,3,CWoman's fury after 'corridor care'
OL,4,Cnightmare at hospital
OL,6,FCorridor care is when patients are
OL,7,Ftreated or held in hospital corridors
OL,8,Ffor more than 12 hours because there
OL,9,Faren't enough beds or space.
OL,11,FAge UK says it is completely
OL,12,Funacceptable and is calling for urgent
OL,13,Fand decisive action from the
OL,14,FGovernment.
OL,16,FSource: Age UK
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
