OL,4,Cnightmare at hospital
OL,6,FThe charity has heard heartbreaking
OL,7,Fstories from older people who it says
OL,8,F"have had to face treatment, tests,
OL,9,Fand life-changing news without privacy
OL,10,Fand in unsafe conditions."
OL,12,FA report revealed some "have suffered
OL,13,Fthe indignity of having to use bedpans
OL,14,Fin corridors, or of lying on the floor
OL,15,Fbecause the chair provided was too
OL,16,Funcomfortable. Tragically, some older
OL,17,Fpeople die before making it to a ward."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
