OL,3,CWoman's fury after 'corridor care'
OL,4,Cnightmare at hospital
OL,6,FCaroline Abrahams, Age UK Charity
OL,7,FDirector, said: "What's happening to
OL,8,Fsome very ill older people when they
OL,9,Fcome to A&E is a crisis hiding in
OL,10,Fplain sight which the Government must
OL,11,Fface up to and take immediate action
OL,12,Fto resolve.
OL,14,F"No one should have to spend their
OL,15,Ffinal days in a hospital corridor
OL,16,Fwhere it's impossible for the staff to
OL,17,Fprovide good, compassionate care, and
OL,18,Fit's truly shocking that this is what
OL,19,Fis happening to some very old people
OL,20,Fin some hospitals, today and every day.
OL,26,@oD@QOU
