OL,6,FAnd as we head into winter, we fear
OL,7,Fthat an already very difficult
OL,8,Fsituation in and around some A&Es will
OL,9,Fget even worse."
OL,11,FHealth Minister Karin Smyth said: "The
OL,12,Fstories in this report are
OL,13,Fheartbreaking. No one should receive
OL,14,Fcare in a corridor - it's
OL,15,Funacceptable, undignified and we are
OL,16,Fdetermined to end it.
OL,26,@sD@cOU
