OL,6,F"To tackle a problem you've got to be
OL,7,Fhonest about it. For the first time,
OL,8,Fthe NHS will measure and publish the
OL,9,Fnumber of patients waiting in
OL,10,Fcorridors. Sunlight is the best
OL,11,Fdisinfectant.
OL,13,F"To give patients the care they
OL,14,Fdeserve, we're investing #450 million
OL,15,Fto build same day urgent and emergency
OL,16,Fcare centres , buying 500 new
OL,17,Fambulances, building 40 new mental
OL,18,Fhealth crisis centres, and giving NHS
OL,19,Fleaders on the ground more power to
OL,20,Fdeliver local solutions.
